<p><strong>Addendum 001.11:</strong> Agent Ruberson's Statement, January 1944</p>
<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:300px;"><a href="/local--files/twistedgears-kaktus-proposal/transport.jpg" target="_blank"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/twistedgears-kaktus-proposal/transport.jpg" style="width:300px;" alt="transport.jpg" class="image" /></a>
